# Dylan Santiago
Sat, May 03
| 
West Hills Vineyards
Join us for an incredible evening with Dylan Santiago live in our tasting room! With his soulful tunes and dynamic performance, Dylan will set the perfect mood as you enjoy our handcrafted beverages. Don’t miss out on this unforgettable night of music and good times! ## Time & Location
May 03, 2025, 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM
West Hills Vineyards, 4785 Salem Dallas Hwy NW, Salem, OR 97304, USA
